sarva eva tvasau prajñopāyamayatayā maṇḍalamudrārūpo 'vagantavya iti | nanvevaṃ bhāvyabhāvakabhāvanānupapattāvutpanne ca maṇḍale nirdiṣṭe dhyeyadhyāne kiṃ sarvathotpādite eva | netyāha—taddhyeyamityādi |

<commentary>vikṣepa eva na dhyānamiti dhyeyamapi tanna syādityāha—pitarītyādi |
tatsukhaṃ bhujyate svayamiti yathopadeśamajasraṃ yauvanābhiṣekayorvā | evamādimadhyāvasāneṣu yatsukhamanuparatamanubhūyate tatsukhaṃ dhyānamucyate | mahāsukhasyānusmaraṇātkuto vikṣepo yato na dhyānadhyeye | athavā pitarīti gurāvabhiṣekakāle yatprāptamanubhūtaṃ sahajamahāsukhaṃ tadbhujyata ābhujyate svayamanyadāpi | mudrāyogato vā tathaivopabhujyate | yenopabhuktena sukhena maraṇamindrayāṇāṃ nirodhaḥ syādiheti dṛṣṭa eva janmani tatsukhaṃ dhyānamucyate | evaṃbhūtaṃ cotpannayogino dhyāna tathānusmaraṇamātre 'pyupadeśe 'nujñāyata iti |</commentary>